To run the program you should:
1. Put the all the files in the zip under the default path of gcl
2. Under the gcl commond line, input (load "numbrix.lsp")
3. Compile the file by input (compile-file "numbrix.lsp")
4. After compiling the file, input (numbrix) to play the game.
5. You need to choose play mode first. a for AI mode; h for human man-mode
6. then you need to choose the board you want to play and input the board index.
7. When solution finished and succeed, the result will display in the board.
8. Then you will be asked to display the board after each step.
9. And you will be asked to play again.
Enjoy the game!
